<!DOCTYPE document PUBLIC "-//APACHE//DTD Documentation V2.0//EN" "http://forrest.apache.org/dtd/document-v20.dtd">

<document>
  <header>
    <title>POST templeton/mapreduce/jar </title>
  </header>

  <body>

  <section>
   <title>Description</title>
    <p>Creates and queues a standard 
     <a href="http://hadoop.apache.org/mapreduce/">Hadoop MapReduce</a> job.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
   <title>URL</title>
    <p><code>http://</code>www.myserver.com<code>/templeton/v1/mapreduce/jar.json</code></p>
  </section>

  <section>
   <title>Parameters</title>
    <table>
    <tr><th>Name</th><th>Description</th><th>Required?</th><th>Default</th></tr>
    
    <tr><td><strong>jar</strong></td>
        <td></td>
        <td>Required</td>
        <td>None</td>
    </tr>

    <tr><td><strong>class</strong></td>
        <td></td>
        <td>Required</td>
        <td>None</td>
    </tr>

    <tr><td><strong>arg</strong></td>
        <td>Some options for configuration, TBD.</td>
        <td>Optional</td>
        <td>None</td>
    </tr>
    </table>
  </section>

  <section>
   <title>Results</title>
     <p>The mapreduce/jar resource queues your MapReduce job and returns 
       the JSON object:</p>
     <p><code>{"id": JOBID, "info": {"stdout": MESSAGE, "stderr": MESSAGE, "exitcode": CODE}}</code></p>

     <table>
      <tr><th>Name</th><th>Description</th></tr>   
    
      <tr><td><strong>id</strong></td>
        <td>A string containing the job id similar to "job_201110132141_0001".</td>
      </tr>

      <tr><td><strong>info</strong></td>
        <td>A JSON object containing the information returned when the job was queued.</td>
      </tr>

      <tr><td><strong>stdout</strong></td>
      <td>A string containing the result sent to standard out (possibly empty).</td>
      </tr>

      <tr><td><strong>stderr</strong></td>
        <td>A string containing the result sent to standard error (possibly empty).</td>
      </tr>

      <tr><td><strong>exitcode</strong></td>
        <td>A string containing the exitcode returned.</td>
      </tr>
     </table>
  </section> 

  </body>
</document>
